Simple NCurses program.
This is just some really basic modifications to a sample program from here:

  http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/NCURSES-Programming-HOWTO/intro.html#ABOUTPROGRAMS

Requirements:

- gcc
- nemiver (for using the `debug' command)
- ncurses

Setup:

> cd /path/to/project/root
> source env/shell

Building:

> build

Running:

> run

Debugging:

> debug